# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# SIFTER AI — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in keys
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

# OPTION A: Fully Local (no data leaves your machine)
# Install Ollama from https://ollama.com, then run: ollama pull llama3.1:8b
# OLLAMA_MODEL=llama3.1:8b

# OPTION B: Free Cloud APIs (fast, resumes sent to provider — anonymized in transit)
# Cerebras — free at https://cloud.cerebras.ai  (fastest, 2000+ tok/s)
# CEREBRAS_API_KEY=csk-...

# Groq — free at https://console.groq.com
# GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_...

# Google Gemini — free at https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
# GOOGLE_GENERATIVE_AI_API_KEY=AIza...

# Priority order: Ollama → Cerebras → Gemini → Groq
# You can have multiple keys active — the app load-balances across them.
